<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <title>날씨</title>
    <style>
        .main-content {
            align-items: center;
        }
        .weather-card {
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: auto;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
            background: #FFFFFF;
        }
        .weather-card p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .weather-card .location {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .weather-card .temp {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
	.weather-card .icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin-top: -10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .cta-message {
            margin-top: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        h3{
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="cta-message">
            <h3>날씨를 확인하고 세탁하세요!</h3>
        </div>
        <h2>현재 날씨</h2>
        <% if (weatherData) { %>
            <div class="weather-card">
                <div class="location"><%= weatherData.name %> / <%= weatherData.sys.country %></div>
                <div class="temp"><%= weatherData.main.temp %> ℃</div>
		<img class="icon" src="http://openweathermap.org/img/wn/<%= weatherData.weather[0].icon %>@2x.png" alt="Weather Icon">
		<p><%= weatherData.weather[0].description %></p>
            </div>
        <% } else if (error) { %>
            <p><%= error %></p>
        <% } else { %>
            <p>날씨 정보를 가져오는 중...</p>
        <% } %>
    </div>
</body>
